{
  "stem": "5810.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, we took an apartment in, in the area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at that time, at liberation, a lot of entertainment cafes opened up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Americans and the British soldiers had places to go and there was a lot of joy, and a lot of activity, and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the things that a lot of cafes were doing, and I guess you call it today in the United States, karaoke type and contests.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had dancing and singing contests and things of that sort for money prizes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I guess from my father being a cantor, I was blessed with a pretty good voice at that time, and I was a young kid.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother, since we had no clothes, we had absolutely nothing, had made clothing in the uniform style from blankets we found on the streets and blankets that the American GIs used to handout on the street.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so she made those little uniforms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I looked, I guess, cute.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had a pretty good voice, and I entered a lot of contests, singing contests.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In these different cafes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I suppose because of my age and because my voice wasn't too terrible I won a lot of those contests.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So some of that money came in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I must also say that my sister and I, we didn't have a whole lot of pride at that point.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had to survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I guess today you'd call it begging, but on the street, we didn't mind asking for money from the GIs and-- for food, or chocolate, or anything of the sort.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But still, we needed to pay the rent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For a while, we moved around a bit whenever the rent was due.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who cared?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
